Package: heteff
Type: Package
Title: Simple GRF Workflows for Heterogeneous Effects
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Dai",
      family = "Dai",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "daik54015@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Provides a simple interface around three generalized random
    forest estimators: grf::causal_forest(), grf::causal_survival_forest(),
    and grf::instrumental_forest(). The package returns reusable effect
    tables, subgroup summaries, explanation-tree outputs, variable-importance
    tables, diagnostics, and a compact set of plots for heterogeneous causal
    effect analysis.
URL: https://dai540.github.io/heteff/,
    https://github.com/dai540/heteff
